# Finalizing RBAC Boundaries

This plan completes the industrial-grade Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) implementation for the ICS Border Control System. We are establishing clear boundaries between operational execution (Officers) and tactical Oversight (Supervisors/Administrators).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Border Officers** will no longer be able to access the **Reports (History)** or **National Watchlist** modules. They will maintain full access to **Traveler Processing** and **Database Search** (targeted queries).
> **Supervisors** and **Administrators** maintain full access to all modules, including the audit-heavy Reports page.

