## Open Questions

- Should Officers be able to see the Dashboard stats (Total Processed, Today's Entries)? (Proposed: Yes, for situational awareness).
- Should Officers be able to *view* the Watchlist without being able to *manage* it? (User requested "wrong same value" fix earlier, implying we should separate these concerns. Proposed: Hide Watchlist for Officers to prevent data scraping, rely on automated flags during processing).

